      <title>无人机竞赛升温 朝鲜推出自杀式攻击无人机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/north-korea-unveils-suicide-attack-drones-as-uav-race-heats-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜推出了新型自杀式攻击无人机，领导人金正恩呼吁加强使用技术手段实施打击，并将人工智能纳入武器计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/north-korea-unveils-suicide-attack-drones-as-uav-race-heats-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 03:00:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新规定使佐科威之子无法参加印尼地方选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/new-rules-shut-jokowi-s-son-out-of-indonesia-s-regional-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印尼选举委员会颁布了新规定，实际上终结了总统佐科·维多多的小儿子参加11月地区选举的任何机会，这一前景引发了上周的大规模抗议活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/new-rules-shut-jokowi-s-son-out-of-indonesia-s-regional-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 02:42:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>载有受制裁俄罗斯液化天然气的油轮试图进行船舶转运</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/tanker-carrying-sanctioned-russian-lng-attempting-ship-transfer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一艘受到制裁的液化天然气油轮似乎正在将运往俄罗斯的货物转移到地中海的另一艘船上，这表明莫斯科将竭力规避美国的行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/tanker-carrying-sanctioned-russian-lng-attempting-ship-transfer</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 02:00:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登助手到访，中国将提高对台关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/china-says-it-ll-raise-taiwan-tariffs-with-visiting-biden-aide</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国家安全顾问杰克·沙利文本周访华时，中国将提出与台湾有关的问题以及关税等“武断措施”，此行旨在维持地缘政治对手之间的对话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/china-says-it-ll-raise-taiwan-tariffs-with-visiting-biden-aide</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 01:06:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>无论谁入主白宫，韩国都认为美国站在自己一边</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/south-korea-sees-us-by-its-side-regardless-of-who-is-in-white-house</link>
      <description><![CDATA[首尔一位高级官员称，韩国政府并不担心哪位候选人赢得美国总统大选，因为无论谁入主白宫，韩国政府都希望与他合作，共同应对朝鲜的核威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/south-korea-sees-us-by-its-side-regardless-of-who-is-in-white-house</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 22:00:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>首席执行官在法国被拘留后，Telegram 表示其遵守欧盟法律</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/telegram-says-it-abides-by-eu-laws-after-ceo-detained-in-france</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周日，Telegram 对法国拘留首席执行官帕维尔·杜罗夫 (Pavel Durov) 的理由提出质疑，杜罗夫是该通讯应用程序的亿万富翁联合创始人，上周末在巴黎机场被拘留。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/telegram-says-it-abides-by-eu-laws-after-ceo-detained-in-france</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 21:40:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加纳副总统表示将签署反 LGBTQ 法案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/ghana-vice-president-says-he-d-sign-anti-lgbtq-bill-into-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果加纳副总统马哈穆杜·巴武米亚 (Mahamudu Bawumia) 在 12 月的总统选举中获胜，他将颁布一项法案，要求对认定为 LGBTQ 的人判处三年监禁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/ghana-vice-president-says-he-d-sign-anti-lgbtq-bill-into-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 21:34:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列轰炸黎巴嫩阻止袭击 中东局势紧张</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/mideast-on-edge-after-israel-bombs-lebanon-to-thwart-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一百架以色列战机飞越黎巴嫩南部，以所谓的先发制人的打击摧毁了真主党数千个导弹发射器，几个小时后，中东地区准备迎接一场可能涉及伊朗及其盟友民兵的扩大战火。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/mideast-on-edge-after-israel-bombs-lebanon-to-thwart-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 16:18:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯导弹击中乌克兰酒店，路透社安全顾问死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-25/5-people-die-in-shelling-of-a-russian-border-region-while-russian-fire-hits-a-hotel-with-reporters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基辅，乌克兰（美联社）——该通讯社证实，一枚俄罗斯导弹击中乌克兰城市克拉马托尔斯克的一家酒店，导致一名与路透社记者团队一起工作的英国安全顾问身亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-25/5-people-die-in-shelling-of-a-russian-border-region-while-russian-fire-hits-a-hotel-with-reporters</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 10:22:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列称对黎巴嫩真主党发动了更多空袭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-25/urgent-israel-says-it-is-staging-airstrikes-inside-lebanon-targeting-the-shiite-militia-hezbollah</link>
      <description><![CDATA[耶路撒冷（美联社）——一位美国官员称，在开罗举行的一轮高层会谈旨在达成停火和人质协议，至少暂时结束以色列和哈马斯在加沙地带长达 10 个月的战争，但会议于周日结束，未达成最终协议。但未来几天，会谈将继续在较低级别进行，以弥合剩余的分歧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-25/urgent-israel-says-it-is-staging-airstrikes-inside-lebanon-targeting-the-shiite-militia-hezbollah</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 02:23:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
